---
globs: ['**/*.css', '**/*.scss']
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use Flexbox and Grid for layout.
- Use CSS custom properties (variables) for consistent theming. All available variables are in ./packages/ui/src/styles/tokens folder.
- Use mobile-first approach for responsive design.
- Use media queries mixins to create responsive layouts from ./packages/ui/src/styles/_breakpoints.scss file.
- Avoid !important; use specificity to manage styles.
- Use focus styles to indicate focus state.
